{"tid":2348311,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【新冠肺炎】全球抗疫致濫用抗生素 世衛警告將造成無法治癒「超級淋病月蛾」","createTime":"2020-12-31T15:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T23:20:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b940b9d9b266eda82baf4f585a61f168b8753a56","tid":2348311,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:49:12.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎全球大流行已達一年，至今已造成全球近 180 萬人死亡。雖然各國都努力抗疫，但世界衛生組織（WHO）專家警告，疫情期間人們過度使用抗生素，許多性傳染疾病大幅增加抗藥性，當中包括性病「超級淋病」，未來有可能無法治癒。<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織（WHO）專家警告，疫情期間人們過度使用抗生素，許多性傳染疾病大幅增加抗藥性<br />\n當中包括性病「超級淋病」，未來有可能無法治癒<br />\n除非有明確的醫學需求，不然不該在新冠肺炎患者身上濫用抗生素<br />\n【相關報道】超級細菌可在太空存活 3 年 承受輻射量高人類 3000 倍<br />\n<br />\n每年全球有超過 9,000 萬人罹患淋病，雖然多數病例在非洲地區，但西方國家的患病人數也以劇烈的幅度在增長。WHO 警告，因為現在有越來越多新冠肺炎確診病例，使用過度的抗生素，讓這些性病也因此產生強大的抗藥性。<br />\n<br />\nWHO 專家警告，在全球對抗新冠肺炎的過程中，醫療系統過度使用抗生素，會加劇淋病等性傳播疾病對於抗生素的抗藥性，培養出更多如超級淋病等超級細菌，進而導致這些疾病很快變得無法治療。<br />\n<br />\nWHO 抗藥性專家 Dr Hanan Balkhy 表示，不應忽略濫用抗生素治療新冠肺炎所造成的高度風險。在大多數的新冠肺炎病患身上，使用這些抗生素來治療，並無法治療他們或者改善他們的症狀，但是會讓患者體內存在有細菌產生更高的抗藥性。她指除非有明確的醫學需求，不然不該在新冠肺炎患者身上濫用抗生素。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2840020?fbclid=IwAR0snnDwOfkjyVCucVvEIqvh2JpSmKXYcG6dT_Ti7oFoNcAaRNMkKHDxEHc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2840020%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0snnDwOfkjyVCucVvEIqvh2JpSmKXYcG6dT_Ti7oFoNcAaRNMkKHDxEHc&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=8377d15c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2840020?fbclid=IwAR0snnDwOfkjyVCucVvEIqvh2JpSmKXYcG6dT_Ti7oFoNcAaRNMkKHDxEHc</a>"},{"pid":"602d4acee744bce5dd226383a5f043c253962796","tid":2348311,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"超級淋病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁過super sailmoon"},{"pid":"c91d1b38fbdc29782de16f562865ace6a22142b6","tid":2348311,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"香港一早有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4522d731a30005d72b6e229ecddd0e7411a865be","tid":2348311,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a93405796c717a3bfa4bce1a6a9ea3a4e05707c","tid":2348311,"uid":331551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:24:40.000Z","msg":"用練獄之火燒呢隻777千萬年<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2495a55efed54eef457eee35b0410af57a7b9d","tid":2348311,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:37:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b6180e36c27d03e3e8cdcd45ad835e176985ef","tid":2348311,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T23:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}